#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean.md:9
msgid ""
"`weighted_mean` calcola la media aritmetica semplice oppure, se forniti, la media pesata con pesi"
" strettamente positivi."
msgstr ""
"`weighted_mean` computes the simple arithmetic mean or, if provided, the weighted mean with "
"strictly positive weights."

